{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175950/extras/enter_the_mindfudge3.png?t=1740418699\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ezrebeth is an old, bitter recluse who finds herself constantly invaded by her peculiar relatives during the winter holidays. Oh, and she's stuck in a time loop! Investigate, interview and cross-reference as you attempt to figure out what's going on in this surreal visual novel. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175950/extras/fDyFZd.png?t=1740418699\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175950/extras/jvj58H.png?t=1740418699\" /> <strong>Enter</strong> a one-of-a-kind narrative full of domestic drama, light horror, witty puns and deep, resonating themes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175950/extras/jvj58H.png?t=1740418699\" /> <strong>Meet</strong> the Casarecce family, a host of memorable characters to interview and/or interrogate as you uncover the truth behind the mysterious time loop!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175950/extras/jvj58H.png?t=1740418699\" /> <strong>Three</strong> games in one! Unlock two additional episodes after completing the main story, which further expand on the characters and the strange world they find themselves in (total playtime: 5-8 hours)! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175950/extras/jvj58H.png?t=1740418699\" /> <strong>Beautiful</strong> and unique artwork drawn by hand, all available to view in a dedicated gallery of memories! </p><p class=\"bb_paragra